{"tid":1078404,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【馬場羅生門】要求擺風水陣遭拒！名人馬主謾罵練馬師半小時","createTime":"2019-03-26T09:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T07:52:49.000Z","uid":58552,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"56284b136cada56ce6cf573bd377707e4739261f","tid":1078404,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"今日（26日）沙田馬場內的話題除圍繞「巴基之星」及「紅衣醒神」試閘的表現外，還出現一宗羅生門事件，據報內容涉嫌謾罵練馬師半小時。<br />\n<br />\n所謂人算不如天算，據了解剛周日（24日）的沙田賽事，一位常出現娛樂版，太太是靚女的知名人士馬主，其愛駒當日大敗多個馬位，賽後他向所屬的華人練馬師開火謾罵，過程大約半小時。<br />\n<br />\n據悉爭執內容之一，包括馬主希望在馬房擺設風水陣，而增加愛駒未來勝出的機會，但該華人練馬師因不相信有關學說而拒絕，之後馬主大動肝火，更將愛駒兩次大敗的因由，推諉至華人練馬師練馬功力不濟，更疑似有點威嚇廐主成份。<br />\n<br />\n消息在馬圈流傳出去後，據悉不少練馬師都替該同袍感不值，故該駒若拉倉，練馬師們擬考慮集體拒收該兩戰大敗的馬匹，為同袍發聲表達不滿；同時該練馬師沒猜到以馬主平日的溫文形象，竟會在對話中如此兇惡，故未曾保存任何錄音證據，或事件最終演化成有理說不清的情況。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》向馬會及相關人士了解事件，該位知名人士馬主只答了一句：「唔回應啦」，而事件中的練馬師今日已起程去了外地，為他旗下馬匹日內遠征大賽事宜打點。<br />\n<br />\n聽講本身搵呢個練馬佬都係貪佢個名夾五行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ab93caca0536f73e671602d8803b4d4b0caba2","tid":1078404,"uid":6435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:32:08.000Z","msg":"邊個華人練馬師去杜拜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f1ba27c35d9739072bed0284d05fa6a1f4eb0f","tid":1078404,"uid":86592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"姓李？"},{"pid":"90cf197aec4205af84b3845a95271e763fec9cc7","tid":1078404,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70ab93caca0536f73e671602d8803b4d4b0caba2","tid":1078404,"uid":6435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:32:08.000Z","msg":"邊個華人練馬師去杜拜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:35:08.000Z","msg":"個名入面有 金木水火土元素果個"},{"pid":"19098d7297cd3a87194e41cf206077207937d20b","tid":1078404,"uid":6435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"90cf197aec4205af84b3845a95271e763fec9cc7","tid":1078404,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70ab93caca0536f73e671602d8803b4d4b0caba2","tid":1078404,"uid":6435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:32:08.000Z","msg":"邊個華人練馬師去杜拜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:35:08.000Z","msg":"個名入面有 金木水火土元素果個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"原來個馬主係棄糟糠果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fcfede845ffce7c5fc3b6f022afbb867cbfdc1","tid":1078404,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:38:43.000Z","msg":"其實應該聽佢講擺陣，再輸就無得賴"},{"pid":"623d20209391be0515f70496c2a45c0933ada8b1","tid":1078404,"uid":42133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"呢條風水佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab332467c9c47f733f9a7cd8a2b277c441421d3","tid":1078404,"uid":179967,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"85fcfede845ffce7c5fc3b6f022afbb867cbfdc1","tid":1078404,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:38:43.000Z","msg":"其實應該聽佢講擺陣，再輸就無得賴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:40:24.000Z","msg":"要搵理由總搵到 佢可以話練馬師專登害鳩佢<br />\n你想個信風水既人講咩道理"},{"pid":"f6ef59c62b3f062b65aec1d8bb3d207002d0745d","tid":1078404,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:41:41.000Z","msg":"李丞責？"},{"pid":"350f9a34f5a6b0283204d48dc411533508b2f1b5","tid":1078404,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aab332467c9c47f733f9a7cd8a2b277c441421d3","tid":1078404,"uid":179967,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"85fcfede845ffce7c5fc3b6f022afbb867cbfdc1","tid":